snippet.title: Trials Frontier -- Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download for FREE now!
App Store: http://bit.ly/1scRQCx
Google Play: http://bit.ly/1n1eCxi

Trials Frontier is now  available on iPhone, iPad & iPod touch!

Explore a vast world on your motorcycle. Compete against your friends on Global Leaderboards. Master physics-based tracks to challenge the world's top riders for the best times. Race your motorcycle through a world of adventure, crazy characters, and unfairly addictive tracks!.

See more on http://trialsgame.com/

Play more at http://appstore.com/ubisoft
And join your community!
Facebook http://facebook.com/UbisoftMobileGames
Twitter http://twitter.com/ubisoftmobile
